      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nProbably lots of places where we can reduce memory usage on the client.  It hasn't been a big issue on most of the systems we run on these days (with tens or hundreds of GB of RAM), but I'd be happy to see more patches to reduce memory usage where it isn't needed.",
